In opening study I have briefly looked at this possibility. It appears Awkward, but is actually not a bad choice; it is just not commonly played. To stifle my curiousity, I checked the game databases here on GameKnot. It has, apparently, never been played in any of their "world" database games; and only been played once here on GameKnot- a drawn game against the top gameknot player Cyrano.
